<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
An advanced, many-functioned <a title="trackball" class="nonexistent" href="http://printwiki.org/trackball">trackball</a> used for videogames developed on the <a title="CD-i" class="nonexistent" href="http://printwiki.org/CD-i">CD-i</a> platform. See <a title="Compact Disc-Interactive" class="nonexistent" href="http://printwiki.org/Compact_Disc-Interactive">Compact Disc-Interactive</a>. 
</p>
